{"tid":183212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馮驊：選管會不是事事都查","createTime":"2017-04-02T01:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T02:41:03.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ffce67b2c10c5031c4e790ea0eb4962aa6934cf6","tid":183212,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T01:45:44.000Z","msg":"選舉管理委員會主席馮驊在選舉前巡視票站，他無回應特首梁振英連日來評論選舉，是否會影響選舉的公平公正。<br />\n<br />\n馮驊表示，選管會不是事事都查，要視乎證據做決定，又強調選管會監察功能亦要跟程序，香港是有言論自由，守法是底線。"},{"pid":"02f6c7210cbff8a075048bd71a9ba25526904556","tid":183212,"uid":29340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T01:50:59.000Z","msg":"唔怪之得掌心雷呢d小事唔撚查啦，連選民資料失竊都可以話唔查"},{"pid":"f29c635bcd0f2db1bb2fcdb1589584dcda60491f","tid":183212,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T02:02:39.000Z","msg":"咩事先查"},{"pid":"b3afe06abdf568a4d16dd269a1004e33b1bb9e1a","tid":183212,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T02:06:25.000Z","msg":"中國式選舉"},{"pid":"65bb90324f0b92c4b8665c907f3ecb4789c19c98","tid":183212,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T02:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4124b8aa5431302261b04741f78c2119b742a378","tid":183212,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T02:41:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.anyanother.com/data/73533.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.anyanother.com%2Fdata%2F73533.jpg&h=3cd174db&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}